            "title": "盤中速報 - 定穎投控(3715)股價拉至漲停，漲停價203.5元，成交72,300張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>定穎投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)27日11:09上漲18.5元，股價漲停報203.5元，委買17,053張，成交72,300張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為一般投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>定穎投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌2.89%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.05%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+3,248 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+3,320 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+1,205 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1,277 張</li> <li>融資增減：-7,174 張</li> <li>融券增減：-618 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6397977",
